The engine pool was committed to trunk in r12924. It removes the fixed engine type limits and allows having multiple NewGRF vehicle sets in one game when using the patch option "dynamic_engines". The first stable release to include this feature is [[OpenTTD 0.7.0/Fr|OpenTTD 0.7.0].